OL,3,CArchaeological 'jigsaw' reveals 2,000-
OL,4,Cyear-old Roman wall paintings in London
OL,6,FIt is believed the frescoes once
OL,7,Fdecorated at least 20 internal walls
OL,8,Fbetween AD 40 and 150, before the
OL,9,Fbuilding was demolished and the wall
OL,10,Fplaster dumped into a pit before the
OL,11,Fstart of the third century.
OL,13,FBut now the reconstruction of the wall
OL,14,Fart has shed further light on high
OL,15,Fsociety in Roman Britain.
