OL,3,CArchaeological 'jigsaw' reveals 2,000-
OL,4,Cyear-old Roman wall paintings in London
OL,6,FInspiration for the wall decorations
OL,7,Fwas taken from other parts of the
OL,8,FRoman world ` such as Xanten and
OL,9,FCologne in Germany, and Lyon in France.
OL,11,FIt took three months for Mola senior
OL,12,Fbuilding material specialist Han Li to
OL,13,Flay out all the fragments and
OL,14,Freconstruct the designs to their
OL,15,Foriginal place.
OL,17,FHe said: "This has been a 'once-in-a-
OL,18,Flifetime' moment, so I felt a mix of
OL,19,Fexcitement and nervousness when I
OL,20,Fstarted to lay the plaster out.
