OL,3,CArchaeological 'jigsaw' reveals 2,000-
OL,4,Cyear-old Roman wall paintings in London
OL,6,F"The result was seeing wall paintings
OL,7,Fthat even individuals of the late
OL,8,FRoman period in London would not have
OL,9,Fseen."
OL,11,FSpeaking to the Today programme on BBC
OL,12,FRadio 4, Mr Li said: "When you are
OL,13,Flooking at thousands of fragments of
OL,14,Fwall paintings every day, you start to
OL,15,Fcommit everything to memory.
OL,17,F"You are sometimes working when you
OL,18,Fare sleeping as well.
